property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT <%=sourceSystem%>  || 'Vendor_' || "LFA1"."MANDT" || "LFA1"."LIFNR" AS "ID",
       "LFA1"."LAND1"                                                      AS "Country",
       "LFA1"."NAME1"                                                      AS "Name",
       "LFA1"."ORT01"                                                      AS "City",
       CASE WHEN "LFA1"."VBUND" IS NULL THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END           AS "InternalFlag",
       "LFA1"."LIFNR"                                                      AS "Number",
       'SAP'                                                               AS "SourceSystemType",
       "LFA1"."MANDT"                                                      AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "LFA1" AS "LFA1"
         LEFT JOIN "USR02" AS "USR02"
                   ON "LFA1"."MANDT" = "USR02"."MANDT"
                       AND "LFA1"."ERNAM" = "USR02"."BNAME"
